import { Button, Box } from '@material-ui/core'
import TextField from '@material-ui/core/TextField'
export default () => {
    return (
        <Box component='span' m={1}>
            
            <Button color='primary'>Hello NEXT</Button>
            <form>
                <TextField
                    id="date"
                    label="start"
                    type="date" 
                    defaultValue="2020-06-01"
                    >

                    </TextField>
            </form>

        </Box>
    )
}
